  "title": "CNC Programmer",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Fabricate parts to meet customer's requirements/standards as per their drawings.</li><li>Run production according to production schedules and output targets.</li><li>Ensure that parts fabricated meet delivery schedules.</li><li>Perform regular cleaning and maintenance of the machines and equipment.</li><li>Perform 5S and cleaning of the work area on a daily basis.</li><li>Contribute to quality and output improvement efforts.</li></ul><p></p><p>Job Requirements:</p><ul><li>Ability to understand engineering drawings and technical instructions</li><li>Knowledge of using measurement instruments to verify part dimensions</li><li>Possess good attitude and teamwork</li><li>Able to work independently and as a team</li><li>Handles multi-tasking and stress well</li><li>Commitment to safety, organization, and quality compliance</li></ul>",
